tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE VoterTurnout (
    voter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    voter_name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    precinct_id INT,
    vote_status VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE voter_turnout (
    voter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    vote_status VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE demographics (
    voter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(100),
    education_level VARCHAR(50),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
    income_level VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE voter_demographics (
  voter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  voter_name VARCHAR(255),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  location VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE voting_history (
  voter_id INT,
  election_name VARCHAR(255),
  election_date DATE,
  vote_status VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE election_districts (
  district_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  district_name VARCHAR(255),
  total_voters INT,
  voting_location VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE election_candidates (
  candidate_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  candidate_name VARCHAR(255),
  party_affiliation VARCHAR(50),
  election_district_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE VoterDemographics (
    voter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    address VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE VoterTurnout (
    voter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    election_date DATE,
    voted BOOLEAN,
    precinct_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE PrecinctInfo (
    precinct_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    precinct_name VARCHAR(50),
    city VARCHAR(50),
    state VARCHAR(2)
)

CREATE TABLE ElectionResults (
    election_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    election_date DATE,
    total_votes INT,
    winner_name VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE DemographicAnalysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    voter_id INT,
    age_group VARCHAR(10),
    voter_turnout BOOLEAN,
    analysis_date DATE
)
